      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for these. i like the first one most. i'm also seeing a lot of people online arguing about whether businesses should even be doing this stuff or if it's just politics. some people think it's super important and others think it's unnecessary or divisive. since you're a marketing expert, what do you think is the best way to frame it so we don't alienate anyone?",
