      "content": "that makes sense. i guess i just wonder, though... if i use the \"everyone belongs\" angle, am i basically just taking a side in a culture war? i feel like i'm walking a tightrope. is there any actual risk that people will see it as purely political, or is the whole debate over whether DEI is \"good\" or \"bad\" just a distraction?",
